        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-26 14:47:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> I mean, check \"usage\" of default constructor. As I can see, none of them are used.\nYes,you're right but most of them required for tests with com.google.code.beanmatchers.BeanMatchers#hasValidGettersAndSetters and com.google.code.beanmatchers.BeanMatchers#hasValidBeanConstructor\nEither we need to reconsider its usage or let default constructors used only for tests.\nWhat do you think about it?",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "071a2d4daaf2650bd2ca7254fbbbc6ae69e13e9e",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5562,
          "name": "Vasyl Razinkov",
